The OML Proxy Server
====================

This directory contains the code for the OML proxy server. The proxy
implements a "server" that collects measurements from clients which
are then forwarded onto an actual OML server.

message_queue.c

   Implement a FIFO message queue containing cbuffer (see
   ${OMLROOT}/lib/shared/cbuf.h) objects.

oml2-proxy-server.c

   Implement the proxy server's top-level main() and its supporting
   functions.

proxy_client.c

   Functions to manage the Client structure.

receiver.c

   Functions responsible for implementing the receive loop that reads
   stores meessages in the message queue.

sender.c

   Implements half-async sender which uses a background thread to send
   messages to the OML server.

session.c

   Session management functions.
